<F P=101> Yugoslavia, Kosovo </F>
<H3> <TI>   Serbs Deploy Tanks, Troops Near Glogovac </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0303115194 Tirana ATA in English 1112 GMT 3 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU0303115194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tirana, March 3 (ATA) -- Some 13 tanks and 10 
military trucks with Serbian officers and soldiers were deployed 
on March 1, 16:00 pm, in Cukat e Komoranit, near Glogovac, in 
Kosova, according to the Information Commission of the Glogovac 
Democratic League of Kosova. 
  200 Serbian soldiers were deployed also in the "Silcapor" 
factory in Kacanik as well as some tanks and heavy artillery of 
various sizes. According to the latest reports the Serbian 
soldiers are going to stay for a long time at the factory 
because from the beginning the Serbian officers and soldiers 
have been very interested in comfortable living conditions. 

</TEXT>

