<F P=102>  AU0503171194 Tirana Radio Tirana Network in Albanian 1430 
GMT 5 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0503171194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana Radio Tirana Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Public Order Ministry spokesman reports that on 
the eve of the trial of former Prime Minister Fatos Nano 
yesterday, despite warnings by the Public Order Ministry, former 
Interior Minister Gramoz Ruci mobilized groups of Enverists 
[Enver Hoxha followers] and former State Security officers and 
tried to create conflicts among the people in the cities of 
