<H3> <TI>   Sejm Passes Budget Law </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0503111494 Warsaw PAP in Polish 0917 GMT 5 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0503111494 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 5 Mar--The Sejm has adopted the 1994 budget 
law with 289 votes for, 115 against, and 27 abstentions. In a 
vote on the assumptions of the monetary policy for the year 
1994, 286 deputies voted for, 97 were against, and 44 deputies 
abstained. 
  The Sejm has also adopted the law to increase the national 
income. There were 332 deputies for and 59 against; 33 
abstained. 

</TEXT>

